DETERMINISM ANALYSIS
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

Sources of Determinism:

✓ Reproduction:
  - Iteration order: Stable SlotMap handles
  - RNG calls: Deterministic given seed
  - Mutation order: Sequential (no parallel races)
  - Spawn queue: Sorted by parent_index

✓ Spawning:
